====阿不拉老師====
'''阿不拉老師'''（{{lang-en|Mr. Richard Adler}}）是南方公園國民小學的木工課老師，在《{{link-en|槌哥對小凡|Tweek vs. Craig}}》裡，他不斷地回想起自己已逝的未婚妻，嚼了大量的尼古丁口香糖來逃避回憶，最後打算自殺。他把自己放在木工用的[[電鋸|電鋸]]台上，但由於槌哥對小凡的對決，讓阿尼在過程中被電鋸殺死。之後他並沒有顯著的表現，不過經常出現在劇集的背景中，偶爾會有台詞。

====老爹====
'''傑羅姆「老爹」麥可羅伊'''（{{lang-en|Jerome "Chef" McElroy Molitiufunchun}}，或稱'''大廚'''）由[[艾薩克·海耶斯|艾薩克·海耶斯]]配音，是《南方公園》裡少數的非裔美籍人物之一，南方公園國民小學的廚師。在故事初期，當四賤客進到餐廳的時候，他總是會說「你們好啊，崽子！」以關心他們，而他也是四賤客們遇到困擾或需要指導時經常會尋找的對象，不過他的建議不見得對孩子們有幫助。他是個有才華的歌手，有時會以演唱靈魂音樂來回答孩子們的問題，他也曾出過唱片。在海耶斯離開《南方公園》團隊後，大廚在《{{link-en|大廚歸來|The Return of Chef}}》中死亡。大廚的角色設計源自於艾薩克·海耶斯，以及特雷·帕克在科羅拉多就讀大學時實際遇過的餐廳從業人員<ref>{{cite web| url=http://collegeprowler.com/book/university-of-colorado/| title=University of Colorado Students Tell It Like It Is| publisher=collegeprowler.com| accessdate=2009-02-28| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220140029/http://collegeprowler.com/book/university-of-colorado/| archivedate=2009-02-20}}</ref>。而在台灣版中將大廚設定為[[山東|山東]]人，因此讲话也是[[兖菏片|山东西南的腔调]]。

大廚的體型碩大，就算不在工作時也經常戴著廚師帽，穿著寫有「大廚」（CHEF）的白圍裙。直到[[#陶侃|陶侃]]登場並發揮更顯著的作用以前，大廚被描繪為南方-{}-公園裡唯一的黑人居民，由於馬特·斯通和特雷·帕克給這個角色添加了太多黑人的刻板印象，因此他們擔心原本構想的理想配音員[[艾薩克·海耶斯|艾薩克·海耶斯]]、{{link-en|羅·勞斯|Lou Rawls}}和[[貝瑞·懷特|貝瑞·懷特]]不會同意為這個角色獻聲<ref name="ytchef">{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aoCsAcY6qgA&feature=PlayList&p=341593B5C14FDCCE&index=3 |title=Trey Parker and Matt Stone interview (2000) pt 4/5 |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211172736/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aoCsAcY6qgA&feature=PlayList&p=341593B5C14FDCCE&index=3 |archivedate=2015-12-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?id=1055 |title=FAQ Archives |publisher=South Park Studios |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090719165217/http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?id=1055 |archivedate=2009-07-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?id=2780 |title=FAQ Archives |publisher=South Park Studios |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090719165222/http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?id=2780 |archivedate=2009-07-19 }}</ref> 。不過海耶斯讚賞劇本早期的大膽內容，因此接下了這份工作。<ref name="ytchef"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BUZ89b0B6pQ&feature=PlayList&p=341593B5C14FDCCE&index=6 |title=Goin' down to South Park |work=[[Viacom|Viacom]] |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206080933/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BUZ89b0B6pQ&feature=PlayList&p=341593B5C14FDCCE&index=6 |archivedate=2015-12-06 }}</ref>

大廚年輕時曾幫助過許多音樂家走上成名之路，例如[[艾爾頓·強|艾爾頓·強]]和[[肉卷_(歌手)|肉卷]]。雖然他自己沒有成為音樂家，但他的廚師生涯也算是成功<ref name="dirtyslut">{{cite episode |title=[[Cartman's_Mom_Is_a_Dirty_Slut|Cartman's Mom Is a Dirty Slut]] |url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1998-02-25 |season=1 |number=113}}</ref><ref name="chefaid">{{cite episode |title=[[Chef_Aid|Chef Aid]] |url= |series=[[South_Park|South Park]] |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1998-10-07 |season=2 |number=214}}</ref>。此外他不時會為市政提出建言，或指出一些荒謬之處<ref name="timmy">{{cite episode |title=[[Timmy_2000|Timmy 2000]] |url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2000-04-19 |season=4 |number=404}}</ref><ref name="deathcamp">{{cite episode |title=[[The_Death_Camp_of_Tolerance|The Death Camp of Tolerance]] |url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2002-11-20 |season=6 |number=614}}</ref>。例如在《{{link-en|市旗辯論賽|Chef Goes Nanners}}》中，他要求將市旗改成一個能表達種族對立歷史的版本<ref name="nanners">{{cite episode |title=[[Chef_Goes_Nanners|Chef Goes Nanners]] |url= |series=[[South_Park|South Park]] |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2000-07-05 |season=4 |number=408}}</ref>。此外在許多不同的劇集裡，他也曾拯救過南方-{}-公園，有時甚至拯救了整個世界<ref name="pinkeye">{{cite episode |title=[[Pinkeye_(South_Park)|Pinkeye]] |url= |series=[[South_Park|South Park]] |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1997-10-29 |season=1 |number=107}}</ref><ref name="mecha">{{cite episode |title=[[Mecha-Streisand|Mecha-Streisand]] |url= |series=[[South_Park|South Park]] |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1998-02-18 |season=1 |number=113}}</ref><ref name="starvin">{{cite episode |title=[[Starvin'_Marvin_(South_Park)|Starvin' Marvin]] |url= |series=[[South_Park|South Park]] |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1997-11-19 |season=1 |number=107}}</ref><ref name="ithits">{{cite episode |title=[[It_Hits_the_Fan|It Hits the Fan]] |url= |series=South Park|credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2001-06-20 |season=5 |number=502}}</ref><ref name="cancelled">{{cite episode |title=[[Cancelled_(South_Park)|Cancelled]] |url= |series=South Park|credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2003-03-19 |season=7 |number=704}}</ref><ref name="hippie">{{cite episode |title=[[Die_Hippie,_Die|Die Hippie, Die]]|url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2005-03-16 |season=9 |number=902}}</ref>。大廚的雙親住在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]（台灣版改為山東），這兩人僅在《{{link-en|女妖症候群|The Succubus (South Park)}}》和《{{link-en|宇宙超級噁爛王|The Biggest Douche in the Universe}}》裡登場。

大廚的興趣之一是{{link-en|休閒性愛|casual sex}}，無論是在家中或是渡假時，經常可以看到他和不同的年輕女性在一起做愛<ref name="beefcake">{{cite episode |title=[[Weight_Gain_4000|Weight Gain 4000]]|url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1997-08-27 |season=1 |number=102}}</ref>。有次他為了籌措律師費而[[男妓|賣淫]]，幾乎和南方-{}-公園的每個女性都發生過性關係。這個興趣直到他遇見司機阿姨才停止，在《{{link-en|女妖症候群|The Succubus (South Park)}}》裡，大廚和維若妮卡相愛並論及婚嫁，直到婚禮進行途中，大廚才發現維若妮卡的原形是[[魅魔|魅魔]].<ref name="succubus">{{cite episode |title=[[The_Succubus_(South_Park)|The Succubus]]|url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=1999-04-21 |season=3 |number=303}}</ref>，在魅魔死亡後，大廚又回歸了原本的生活。除非大廚正在和女人翻雲覆雨，否則他通常樂意協助孩子們的困擾，而他也是四賤客少數信任的大人及忠實的朋友<ref name="return">{{cite episode |title=[[The_Return_of_Chef|The Return of Chef]]|url= |series=South Park |credits=Trey Parker and Matt Stone |network=Comedy Central |airdate=2006-03-22 |season=10 |number=1001}}</ref> 。四賤客有時會在學生餐廳裡說出自己的困擾，有時會直接到大廚家找他幫忙，劇集初期的問題大多涉及成人與性，而大廚會以靈魂音樂的方式為他們解惑，不過孩子們不見得能理解。

